## Hardware Register Documentation

The Modbus register maps used in drivers (e.g., luna2000_driver.py) are
derived from publicly available technical documentation:

- Huawei SUN2000 Modbus Interface Definition — published by Huawei Technologies
  for integration purposes. No Huawei proprietary code is included.
- SMA Modbus registers — publicly available from SMA developer portal.
- Victron VE.Bus — published by Victron Energy B.V.
- Fronius Modbus TCP — published by Fronius International GmbH.
- SolarEdge SunSpec Model 124 — publicly available SunSpec specification.
- BYD Battery-Box CAN protocol — derived from publicly available documentation.
- Tesla Powerwall 3 Local API — reverse-engineered community documentation;
  no Tesla proprietary code is included.

